'''Hell of the Flaming Rooster''' (鶏地獄, ''torijigoku'', "Rooster Hell") is one of the sixteen lesser hells depicted in the [[Japan]]ese [[Hell Scroll (Nara National Museum)|Hell Scroll]]. The scroll depicts a flying [[rooster]], breathing fire.

