'''Hindu Sanskar Radio''' (also known as '''Asian Plus''' on [[DAB Digital Radio]]) is a Hindu teachings based [[radio station]] broadcast from [[Leicester]]. It is run by volunteers and the local Hindu temples. It transmits on [[DAB Digital Radio]] and from its website. During Hindu religious festivals, it also transmits on analogue radio.

